16:05.298 --> 16:06.538
ALL OF US.

16:06.632 --> 16:10.466
YES, YES,
WE'VE BEEN HAPPY.

16:10.511 --> 16:14.470
TWO WEEKS OF
BORROWED TIME.

16:14.515 --> 16:16.631
