19:20.284 --> 19:21.740
GOOD NIGHT, SWEETHEART.

19:39.011 --> 19:40.513
IT IS...

19:40.596 --> 19:43.054
IT IS BETTER THIS WAY.

19:47.687 --> 19:50.054
