OFTEN ENOUGH.

21:38.214 --> 21:39.500
<i>BUT THAT'S SILLY.</i>

21:39.590 --> 21:40.955
<i>DON'T YOU
KNOW THAT?</i>

21:41.008 --> 21:42.339
