A PSYCHIATRIST.

21:44.678 --> 21:46.464
WELL, SO WHAT?

21:46.514 --> 21:49.222
SO HE TOLD ME HE DIDN'T
THINK I NEEDED THE CLOCK.

21:49.308 --> 21:51.720
AND HE DIDN'T
THINK I WAS CRAZY.

21:51.811 --> 21:53.142
AND YOU KNOW WHAT?

21:53.229 --> 21:54.890
HE WAS RIGHT
AND WE'RE WRONG.

21:54.980 --> 21:59.565
PERSONALLY, I NEVER TRUST
THE PSYCHIATRISTS.

21:59.652 --> 22:03.145
WELL, YOU'RE FROM
ANOTHER GENERATION.

22:03.197 --> 22:04.813
SEE, I LIVE
IN THE PRESENT.

22:04.907 --> 22:06.238
LIVE, I SAID.

22:06.325 --> 22:07.861
LOOK AT ME.

22:07.952 --> 22:11.161
YOU'RE JUST A FIGMENT
OF MY IMAGINATION.

22:11.205 --> 22:13.037
WHY, I CAN SEE
RIGHT THROUGH YOU.

22:17.837 --> 22:20.249
