OF MINE.

23:13.017 --> 23:15.600
NOW, YOU LET ME UP,
LET ME OUT OF THIS BED.

23:15.686 --> 23:16.972
MY GOODNESS,

23:17.062 --> 23:19.599
YOU SHOULDN'T WORRY
ABOUT ME.

23:19.690 --> 23:21.476
COME ON DOWNSTAIRS
AND I'LL GET YOU

23:21.567 --> 23:23.399
